titles.title: Supporting the goals and ideals of Cambodian-American Freedom Day.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Oversight and Government Reform.

bill.summary:
7/31/2007--Introduced.
Supports the goals and ideals of Cambodian-American Freedom Day. Recognizes: (1) the 32nd anniversary of the arrival of the first Cambodian immigrants to the United States; and (2) the contributions Cambodian-Americans have made to the United States.
